Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:12.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你从未受过伤时  战斗很容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's easy to fight when you've never been hurt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  你不可战胜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Until it happens, you're invincible...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:21.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但每次战斗都有风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But with every fight, there's a risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时你会因为受伤而退出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and sometimes you're sidelined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你不知道何时才能恢复时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The road to recovery is long--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复之路很漫长  没有尽头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}endless when it's not clear if you can recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些日子  我会忘记自己是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some days, I lose sight of who I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我忘不了我的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I can't forget what my mission is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇静  鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Easy, easy, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:05.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再高点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再高点  好的  鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Higher, higher. Okay, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:03.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Watch it, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须保持希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have to keep the hope alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}冷冻人在做准备\N威尔福德有动作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然能改变现状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I can still make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不行的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那死而复生又有何意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then what was coming back from the dead for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我数着日子  祈祷能恢复到从前的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I count the days and pray to be whole again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在雪国列车上的朋友团聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}back with my people on Snowpiercer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}1,034 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:00.39,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs36\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,85)}雪国列{\fsp0}车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:00.39,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第五{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"保持希望{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从雪国列车回来后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hasn't stopped playing her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就一直在放她的歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}since we got back from Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子度过的最棒的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the only best day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He has lost his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看他让我们读什么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you see what he has us reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥德丽小姐太耀眼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, Miss Audrey was so dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他思念着她  他的爱人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's pining for her, his great love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你一直念着倒数第二个澳大利亚人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you've been pining over the second-to-last Australian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他叫默里  -默里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- His name's Murray. - Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}《蝴蝶梦》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的读者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear readers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:17.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下你的书  为读书俱乐部磨练你的妙语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}lay down your tomes and sharpen your bon mots for book club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道这意味着什么  -靠  我还没看完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes, you know what that means. - Shit, I haven't finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了他第一任妻子  房子烧毁  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He killed his first wife and the house burns down. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和威尔福德发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened with you and Wilford?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这工作时  你救了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I worked here, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎么拯救自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You knew how to save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你和威尔福德之间的事知之甚少  这让我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The little I do know about you and Wilford has me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛睁得很大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My eyes are wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟上次不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is nothing like the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:55.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海德伍德医生  海德伍德医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dr. Headwood, Dr. Headwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Emelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刮了胡子的达米安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Damien with the nice, trim jib.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉克斯  来吧  大家都来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alex, come in, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁想先来说说你对《蝴蝶梦》的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who wants to open with thoughts on our "Rebecca"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你想来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:27.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就别举手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then don't put your hand up then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found her devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对她丈夫的热爱很可悲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to her husband tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坦白说  她丈夫很垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mm. Her husband sucked, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He sucked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个英语文学里最经久不衰作品之一里的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This husband from one of the most enduring works
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in English literature?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Emelia, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我们的旁白女主人公吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you trust our narrator heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对她几乎一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We know almost nothing about her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只知道她年轻  坠入了爱河\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}other than she's young and in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们能体会到她的心态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we do get into her psyche,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体验  她有多嫉妒瑞贝卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}experience how jealous she is of Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不诚实的话  我想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If she wasn't being honest, I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会给我们展示她的缺点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she would show us her ugly traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是忽视了她脑子完全被瑞贝卡占据的事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But that's ignoring how consumed she is by Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不信任自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If she doesn't trust herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们为什么信任她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then why would we ever trust her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excellent point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉亚  你的反驳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Emelia, your rebuttal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她恋爱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's a girl in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这能让她做出疯狂的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That can make you do crazy things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行事异常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and act outside of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们继续讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do continue with the salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I, uh, I find
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们这一对很浪漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the pair of them romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:50.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们的爱情高于一切  -不  绝不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Their love above all else-- - No, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这让人沮丧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I find it quite depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在前列车厢的朋友点灯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our friend uptrain lit a lantern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮  塞克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good work, Sykes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这封请帖送去给奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, send this invitation out to Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}迷人的奥德丽小姐\N我盛情邀请你  在穿越拉萨的紫禁城时与我共进晚餐\N一个充满回忆  满是忠诚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去大爱丽丝的请帖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's an invitation to Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, well, lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我盛情邀请你  在穿越紫禁城时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A cordial invitation to dine together
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-与我共进晚餐  -还有西藏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- as we pass the forbidden city. - But also Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们多年前去过那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We traveled there years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个很大的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're asking an awful lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You good with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解  我们需要保护自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I understand. We need to protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前提是你能保护自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only if you can protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道他不会把门一锁  把你留在那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you know he won't just lock the door and keep you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约瑟夫不会违背我意愿强留我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joseph wouldn't hold me against my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们需要这样做  我能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we need this, and I can do it--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少搞清楚那边的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at least find out what's going on over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是个通讯面板  -只有一颗螺丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is the comms panel. - It's only got one screw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大爱丽丝上  是个红盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On Big Alice, it's a red box
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在他后面引擎的墙上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}attached to a wall in his back engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原型里有个缺陷  不过我们的修复了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was a flaw in the prototype fixed in ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这两根线交换位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You switch these two wires,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能听到他说的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can hear everything he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:12.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会知道自己的通讯设备开启还是关闭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He won't be able to tell if his comms are turned on or off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我留点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, save some for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还多着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plenty where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经好久没有遇到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been quite some time since we've had a patient
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组织损伤如此严重的患者了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with this amount of tissue damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能愈合吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will it heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海德伍德夫妇  借一步说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Headwoods, a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是今晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's happening tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们说好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That wasn't what we agreed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注意  门向内打开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的惊恐症犯了  放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're having a panic attack. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出房间里的五样红色物品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Name five red things in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What--what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出房间里的五样红色物品  赶紧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Name five red things in the room, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血液  血液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Blood, blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tis-tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-桶  -接着说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- B-bucket. - Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}B-button.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的红书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your red book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诀窍在于将痛感外化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The trick is is to externalize the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:34.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别内化  否则会让你瘫痪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't internalize it, or it'll paralyze you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德今晚计划了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's Wilford planning for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海德伍德夫妇看起来不开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Headwoods don't look to pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你惹不起他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They are not people you wanna cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天得先麻醉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll have to put you under for the debridement
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你的肩膀做清创\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on your shoulder today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得再深入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have to go deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:10.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的11号气象气球今早放出去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so our weather balloon number 11 went up this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是好消息  德拉托雷先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that's good news, Mr. De La Torre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以和梅兰妮建立联系时告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let us know when we can announce contact with Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的砰砰声能振奋士气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Her pings do wonders for morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -哈维  你刚才说到哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sorry. - Javi, you were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  数据已经分享给威尔福德了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, so the data has been shared with Wilford
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我们之前同意的那样  梅兰妮能保证结果安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as we agreed. Results are safe with Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:29.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学安全  但我们不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The science is safe, but we are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得知道哪些车厢容易受到外部袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to know which cars are vulnerable to an outside attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有迹象显示威尔福德的冷冻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are indications that Wilford's cold man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:38.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可能另有打算  -什么迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- might be up to something. - What indications?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维修车  任何有舱门的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Breach cars, anything with a port
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-都可能是弱点  对吧  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- might be a weak point, yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有16个维修出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So we have 16 breach exits,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有都能从外部入口把手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all of which we can secure from outside entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're worried about attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们依然敞开大门做交易吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we're still opening the border for trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  交易一如往常不变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, trade will continue as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提尔  你和罗切留下  我有话要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Till, you and Roche stay here. I need a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那有线人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a source over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我想我们都知道是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, I think we can guess who that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你在通过交易进行交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you're communicating through trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她还好吗  -还好  暂时还好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is she all right? - She's fine...for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有所发现  所以我们要继续开放边境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's onto something, which is why we have to keep the border open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么担心威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're all worried about Wilford,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们自己家就麻烦事一大堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we've got our own problems here at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维修工和车尾人斗得你死我活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Breachmen and the Tailies are at each other's throats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱茨手指被砍掉已经过去两周了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been two weeks since Lights' fingers were chopped off,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还没找到一个嫌犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I still don't have a suspect--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个正经的嫌犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a legitimate suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  提尔  不如你请一天假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, Till, why don't you take a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说的对  休息一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's right. Take a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果莱顿先生不想让乘客服务部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Mr. Layton wants to keep Hospitality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道他的诡计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}out of his machinations,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只能不让他知道我们的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'll just have to keep him out of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事还是不知道为好  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some things are need to know, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  比如奥德丽是间谍吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What things? Like Audrey is spying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不觉得那很冒险吗  让他们俩在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He doesn't think that's risky-- putting them two back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们需要知道我不是昨天才出生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People need to realize I wasn't born yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:07.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:15.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特里斯坦  你不再是播音员了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tristan, you are fired from the address service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  扎拉  我们看看你的本事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, Zarah, let's see what you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:27.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我  现在吗  -看你如何应对压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Me? Now? - Mm, poise under pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:35.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早上会犯恶心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Morning sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不早说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这样播音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't do announcements like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们将攀登西藏高原\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Today as we climb the Tibetan Plateau,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:01.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的温度是零下83摄氏度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the temperature outside is -118 degrees centigrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风向是西北偏北\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The wind is north-northwest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风速是30至40节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at 30 to 40 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘客服务部提醒各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hospitality would like to remind you all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:12.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请关注今天的海拔变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to be mindful of the change in elevation today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠窗的乘客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For our window watchers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们将经过拉萨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}today we will be passing Lhasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昔日西藏的著名紫禁城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the famous forbidden city of what was formerly Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:56.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送个邀请函会死啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A simple invite would have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:04.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人  包括你  不经我的允许不能去三等厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing, including you, moves through Third without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你再\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踏入这里一步  你就死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Set foot up here again, you'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这个声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ugh, I hate that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  这是钉子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I know. It's when the staples
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,订进头骨的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}turn in against the skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次  准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One more--ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Layton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的大麻生意喂饱了车尾  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My weed trade feeds the Tail, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这难道不是你给我的原因之一吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that not part of the reason you gave it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, you know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是LJ  那个小变态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was LJ, you know, the little psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子让我害怕  她是你教出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That kid scares me, and she's your cultivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那奥斯维勒呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Osweiller?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不重要  他是匹独狼  是特伦斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forget about him. He's a lone wolf. It's Terence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:50.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是特伦斯  我的兄弟  不能再这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Terence, my brother. This can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的  听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It won't. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会处理的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和赛克斯什么时候打算告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When do you and Sykes plan on telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在前车密谋着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what you're cooking uptrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心点  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Patience, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要发生的事对每个人来说都是惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's coming will be a surprise to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这套对私人晚宴来说合适吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fitting for an intimate evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你看上去很好  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You look fine. - Fine?
