Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:20.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这足以建立气候模型  但是梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's enough to build a climate model, but Melanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:25.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天我都能感受到她的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can feel her out there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:31.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们回去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we turn around for her tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:34.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要照计划发射最后一个探测器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we need to launch our last probe as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让威尔福德知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford can't get wind of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:37.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要让他继续参与任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to keep him on mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:40.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去找梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}going back to get Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:42.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要怎么和乘客们说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what should we tell the passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:45.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在等着我们宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're expecting an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:53.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅兰妮是唯一维系我们团结的因素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie's the one thing that's been keeping us all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:57.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她维系了七年  还是有影响力的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She did it for seven years. It still means something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就撒谎吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So then we lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:05.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了希望而撒的谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lie for hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个你为之奋斗的新世界秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This new world order you fought for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:19.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不向人们口中所说的那么好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}isn't all it's cracked up to be, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都能获得自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a free for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.78,0:24:24.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会更想抓到威尔福德吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd rather have Wilford?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:26.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更想静观其变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd rather sit back and see where the chips fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.49,0:24:30.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  小奥  我没法袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't do that, Oz. There's something about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.46,0:24:38.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我挺想你的  贝丝  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I kind of miss you, Bess. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:44.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有听说任何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You hear anything even slightly solid
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:46.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于维修工袭击车尾人的确凿消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the Breachman attacking that Tailie?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.44,0:24:47.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确凿消息  没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Solid, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, they're good for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.74,0:24:53.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受雇于威尔福德  有组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford hires, organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.72,0:24:57.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样  谁都有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So what? Could be anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.63,0:25:00.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头见  提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See you around, Till.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.27,0:25:06.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭维那两个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Compliments of those two assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:13.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-敬我们伟大的工程师  -说得好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- To our great Engineer! - Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.48,0:25:14.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-波吉  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Boki. - Mm-hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:17.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬我们伟大的工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To our great Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.22,0:25:23.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  这会造成麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, hey, listen, that leads to trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.31,0:25:25.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我巴不得呢  -跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah, I'm hoping. - Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.28,0:25:26.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西给你看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.55,0:25:32.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你想拳击  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You want to spar? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.44,0:25:36.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出乎我的意料  牧师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, not what I was expecting, pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.54,0:25:40.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在酒吧认识你  我只会去最让人意想不到的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just met you in a bar. I go where I'm least expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.36,0:25:58.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就这点能耐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.69,0:26:00.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在学校里赢过很多男生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I beat a lot of boys at the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.24,0:26:02.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.11,0:26:08.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在过去伤害过很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You hurt a lot of people in your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.39,0:26:10.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -人们伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What? - People hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.66,0:26:14.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想感受痛苦  但那不可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't want to feel pain, but it's unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:18.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受苦是人类状态的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Suffering is a part of the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.00,0:26:30.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在不伤害人的情况下享乐  放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't get to joy, to relief, without hurting--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.21,0:26:34.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时伤害你自己  有时是别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sometimes yourself, sometimes others.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.40,0:27:09.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.29,0:27:13.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have Melanie on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.20,0:27:16.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你讲乘客服务部的事项\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, walking you through Hospitality,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.10,0:27:19.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我记起了很多事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it has me remembering all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.82,0:27:22.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要休息一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:26.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Walk with me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.55,0:27:29.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我顺便在脑子里构思下如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as I compose this announcement of false hope
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.10,0:27:30.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给乘客们宣布虚假希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for the passengers in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.20,0:27:40.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不天真  扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, I'm not naive, Zarah--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.76,0:27:44.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来不是  以后也不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never was, never will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.29,0:27:47.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道掌权的人会撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that people in power lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:53.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连我也做过我感到可耻的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even I've done things in teal that I'm ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.89,0:27:58.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了提升乘客们的士气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, a white lie to lift the passengers' spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.74,0:28:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而说的善意谎言不包含在内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}won't be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.28,0:28:04.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这列车上的领袖  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a leader on this train, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.35,0:28:07.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的选择能产生影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your choices make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.10,0:28:19.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要它们能产生影响  扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, I need them to, Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.08,0:28:22.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.17,0:28:32.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得攀登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember us climbing the steps
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.98,0:28:35.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哲蚌寺的阶梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the Drepung Monastery right out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.16,0:28:37.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次看到  真的很美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's so beautiful to see again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.28,0:28:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.96,0:28:44.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都没了  伟大的城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, all gone--great cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:47.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗教  完整的思想流派\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}religions, whole schools of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.99,0:28:49.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The world out there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.70,0:28:51.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}doesn't serve a purpose anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.87,0:28:55.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地我跟那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then, thank goodness I'm with the man
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.97,0:28:58.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造了唯一继续有意义的事物的人在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who invented the one thing that continues to matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.35,0:29:05.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你回到我身边它才有价值  奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's only worth it if you're back by my side, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:09.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开一瓶开胃酒  这样我好逗留久一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then open an aperitif so I can linger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.09,0:29:13.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定能找到点甜的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure I can find something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:54.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.30,0:30:03.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.89,0:30:08.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚说到哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.97,0:30:16.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大爱丽丝  大爱丽丝  这里是雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big Alice, Big Alice, this is Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.51,0:30:18.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.49,0:30:23.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本  是你的鼻音吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ben, is that your nasally voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.35,0:30:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是来确认下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just confirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.50,0:30:27.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天发射了11号气球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We launched the balloon 11 today,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.03,0:30:30.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅兰妮像往常一样连上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, uh, Melanie linked up as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.69,0:30:32.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人着迷  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Riveting stuff, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.56,0:30:34.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这就是为什么气候科学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess that's why climate science
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.37,0:30:35.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直没有受众\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never really found an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.14,0:30:51.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看看点心有什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shall we see what's for dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.13,0:31:10.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.03,0:31:12.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guess that's why I'm sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:21.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不总是适合你  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doesn't really suit you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.29,0:31:24.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时正好有空位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was available.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.33,0:31:26.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.24,0:31:31.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Running the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.23,0:31:41.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事我自己做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are some things I can't do myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.08,0:31:47.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车尾想要因同类相食而吊死我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Tail wanted to hang me for cannibalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.59,0:31:49.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为我担保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you vouched for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:50.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:54.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I made a vow
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.14,0:31:58.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不再在战斗之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never kill outside of combat
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.91,0:32:00.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人  为了做一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}again, to be a...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.18,0:32:04.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做一个更好的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to be a better man, to...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.24,0:32:08.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-变得更善良  -你做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- to have a better heart. - You have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.93,0:32:14.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了当你让我做这样的事之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Except when you ask me to do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.08,0:32:20.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果特伦斯想要利用乔茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Terence is going to try and use Josie
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.21,0:32:22.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来敲诈我  那她就不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to blackmail me, she isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.67,0:32:25.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能失去那边的线人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can't lose our source over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.52,0:32:28.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们的姐妹  派克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she's our sister, Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:43.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人会在雪国列车历史上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ain't no scribe writing Pike's story
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.68,0:32:45.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记录派克的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the history of Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:50.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车尾人的故事会流传更久  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tailie stories live longer, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.56,0:33:08.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚看上去很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You looked good in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.78,0:33:12.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你该保持下去  -也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You should keep it up. - I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.34,0:33:15.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前说的那些话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, that stuff you said earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.44,0:33:19.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于人类伤害自己和别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about humans hurting ourselves and others...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.97,0:33:22.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你真的相信吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Do you believe it? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.25,0:33:26.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不怎么像基督\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doesn't seem very Christlike.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.62,0:33:28.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人都\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know the realities
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.52,0:33:30.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更了解这辆列车的现实状况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of this train better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.84,0:33:34.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过人们对彼此  对自己做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've seen what people do to one another, to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.10,0:33:37.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而一想到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it's depressing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.07,0:33:40.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在世界末日我们都无法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to think that, at the end of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.57,0:33:44.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相善待  就令人抑郁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can't just find a way to be good to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.20,0:33:47.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't look at it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:52.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这辆列车最近经历了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This train has gone through a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.53,0:33:56.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们想要指引  一个依靠的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People want guidance, someone to look to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.62,0:34:01.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that's not Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.31,0:34:02.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你跟他很亲近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you're close to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.45,0:34:07.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在他的带领下我们举步维艰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it hasn't been an easy road under his leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.15,0:34:12.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定也感受到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You must feel it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.73,0:34:19.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酝酿着的改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The change that's brewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.05,0:34:24.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个领袖能妥协的次数有限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A leader can only compromise himself so many times
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.64,0:34:28.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后群众就会失去对他的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before he loses the faith of his flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.75,0:34:34.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得给他时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to give him time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.55,0:34:36.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.12,0:34:41.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者他是错误的领导人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or he's the wrong shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.70,0:34:45.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《耶利米书》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeremiah...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.85,0:34:47.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第50章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chapter 50
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.89,0:34:50.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第6节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}verse 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.25,0:34:55.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的百姓作了迷失的羊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"My people have been lost sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.49,0:34:59.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧人使他们走差路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their shepherds have led them astray"...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.91,0:35:08.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使他们转到山上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Turning them away on the mountains"...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.83,0:35:16.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们从大山走到小山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"From mountain to hill, they have gone"...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.45,0:35:25.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟忘了安歇之处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"They have forgotten their fold."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.51,0:35:49.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.76,0:35:52.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need this to be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.97,0:36:08.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来杀我  你还想要公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You come here to kill me, and you want it to be fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.50,0:36:11.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是车尾的习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a Tail thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.23,0:36:15.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯维勒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Osweiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.76,0:36:19.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.35,0:36:22.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都去散步了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They all took a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.74,0:36:29.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  等下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, man, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.96,0:36:31.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.09,0:36:37.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱顿提出六四分  我可以接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton offered 60/40, right? I can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.83,0:36:39.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会说出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I won't say a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.11,0:36:42.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他女友在大爱丽丝上做间谍的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about his girl over on Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.68,0:36:45.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  特伦斯  我这是出于好意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, Terence, I'm giving you this courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:50.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速安静地搞定  没人乱跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just do this quickly, quietly, and no one comes running.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.33,0:37:02.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.11,0:37:03.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本想要你带着尊严死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted you to do this with honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.62,0:37:07.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  你不用  -安静死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Wait, wait, you don't--wait! - To do this quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.28,0:37:26.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做是对的  安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did the right thing, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.08,0:37:29.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.27,0:37:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.91,0:37:55.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening, Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.96,0:38:01.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早些时候  在高空  我们又一个气象气球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Earlier today, high above us, another of our weather balloons
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.29,0:38:03.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和卡维尔工程师建立了联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}made contact with Engineer Cavill
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.58,0:38:06.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她独自一人在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}out there on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.85,0:38:09.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们前方的路照明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a lone spark lighting the way forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.04,0:38:14.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这辆列车上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On this train,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.42,0:38:17.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对绝望都不陌生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}none of us are strangers to despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.83,0:38:20.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们应该在胜利的时候好好庆祝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we should celebrate these victories when they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.49,0:38:24.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须坚守我们的任务  我们的愿景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We must hold fast to our mission, our vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.72,0:38:26.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.47,0:38:28.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.90,0:38:33.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们准备回去找她的同时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as we prepare to turn around and return to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.16,0:38:38.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起为卡维尔工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let us all say a prayer for Engineer Cavill
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.58,0:38:44.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及未来能在雪国列车之外生活祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and our dreams of a life one day beyond Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.31,0:39:25.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这些喝完就开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, down the hatch with these we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.41,0:39:27.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手术要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long does the procedure take?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.45,0:39:28.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概一小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roughly an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.62,0:39:38.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁我还没忘我得把这个记下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I gotta jot this down before I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.99,0:39:55.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There we are. Nighty night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.81,0:40:05.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个赛克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That Sykes...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.04,0:40:08.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她最近带来的都是坏消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she only brings bad news these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.93,0:40:11.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢她今天的来访\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did not appreciate her visit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.40,0:40:20.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血  组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Blood, tissue...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.93,0:40:26.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桶  楼梯  光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bucket, stairs, lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.60,0:40:30.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-威尔福德一催再催  -我们不会输的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Wilford pushes and pushes. - We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.78,0:40:39.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她动了吗  -我没注意到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Did she move? - I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.25,0:40:40.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.01,0:40:42.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.04,0:40:44.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.81,0:40:45.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.03,0:40:48.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.75,0:40:51.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-今晚就开始了  -嗯  维修工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's starting tonight. - Mm, the Breachmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.26,0:40:54.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这么早就利用他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's using them so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.73,0:40:55.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.14,0:40:58.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能会早早失去一些好实验对象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We could lose some good subjects too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.34,0:41:13.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你把药扔了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw you ditch your meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.58,0:41:16.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做手术的时候并没有昏过去  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You weren't knocked out during that procedure, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.75,0:41:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.46,0:41:26.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.24,0:41:36.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要告诉他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you gonna tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.44,0:41:49.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你知道你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope you know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.57,0:41:59.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边境很快就关了  你不必离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Border's closing soon. You don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:01.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来陪我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.14,0:42:04.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟以前不一样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not the same person anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.88,0:42:07.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样的  你还是从前的你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are. You are the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.65,0:42:10.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听我说  我不会被你击溃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not hearing me. I won't be broken by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.74,0:42:15.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们要继续下去  你得让我击垮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if we're gonna do this, you need to let me break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.12,0:42:18.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think that's possible--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.66,0:42:20.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表面下有太多的冰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}too much ice under the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.67,0:42:22.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不放我进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So if you won't let me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.21,0:42:23.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能改善列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you can't change for the good of the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.87,0:42:27.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我在这干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.42,0:42:28.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Audrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.84,0:42:33.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人都了解我  你也了解莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know me better than anyone, and you know Mr. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.72,0:42:35.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得最后谁会赢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who do you think will come out on top?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.49,0:42:39.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约瑟夫  你在计划什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joseph, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.74,0:42:43.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  我希望在我把车夺回来后你能在我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shh, I want you by my side when I take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.03,0:42:46.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来陪我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay, stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.75,0:42:52.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不肯承认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You won't admit it to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.67,0:42:54.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没有我你如同行尸走肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you're only half alive without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:42:56.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.10,0:42:58.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起时我们充满刺激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Together we're electric,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.69,0:43:00.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每条神经都在燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}every nerve on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.44,0:43:05.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来  奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay with me, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了  老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This one's here, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:14.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以过去了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're clear to pass. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.50,0:43:18.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开  免费贸易来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make way. Free trade coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.16,0:43:23.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  让开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.59,0:43:25.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰尼  别碰  你得等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tiny, get your hands off it. You have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.14,0:43:28.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今晚  维修工
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.99,0:43:29.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西快运完了  还是不见奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that's almost all of it and still no Audrey.
